[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "久しぶりに帰って来たら、行きつけの店が\n潰れちゃってた……王都はすぐ変わるなあ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00740",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "隊長！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00741",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "隊長、クレオ隊長じゃないですか！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00742",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "あなた……！　ケガはもう大丈夫なの？\n重傷だったんじゃ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00743",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おかげでようやく退院できまして。\n他のみんなも一時は危なかったんですけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00744",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "隊長があいつ……ヘルトとかいう奴を\n倒したって聞いて、すっかり元気になりましたよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00745",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "そ、そうなんだ……よかった、\n元気になって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00746",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "あ、でも！　私はもう隊長じゃないよ！\n結局光星隊は発足前に潰れたんだし……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00747",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "なに言ってるんですか、隊長は俺らにとって、\n隊長以外の何者でもないですよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00748",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "だけど、部下をみすみすやられた指揮官なんて、\n隊長にはふさわしく……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00749",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……隊長、どうしたんすか？\nしおらしく大人しくなんて、隊長らしくない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00750",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺たちが負けたことに対して責任を持つのは\nともかく、負い目を感じるのはおかしいですよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00751",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺たちは感謝してるんですよ。\nその後、隊長が仇を取ってくれたって！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00752",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "……こんな私をまだ、隊長って認めてくれるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00753",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "俺たちの隊長はクレオ・ランターナだけです。\n光星隊だって休んでるだけでなくなったわけじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00754",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "勝手に過去にされたら、困ります。\n特殊部隊に入れたって誇りを手に入れたんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00755",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "そうか……それも、そうだよね。\n……ありがとう。本当に……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00756",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ところで……誰がしおらしく大人しいと\nらしくないって？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00757",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "げっ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00758",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ええそうよ、どーせ私は王女様らしくない、\nはねっかえりのじゃじゃ馬ですよー",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00759",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そこまでは言ってないっすよ！！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00760",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "上官への不敬な態度、実に罪深い！\n罰としてお菓子をおごりなさい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00761",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そんな、ただでさえ入院費厳しかったのに……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00762",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "あと、その病院。案内して。\n他のみんなはまだ入ってるんでしょ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00763",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……え？\nええ、それはもちろん、構いませんけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00764",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "入院中もこっそり隠れて食べられる\nそういうお菓子を所望するわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00765",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……ああ、なるほど。はいはい、\n承知いたしました。隊長",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00766",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "騎士",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "入院中は食いたいもん食えないっすからね。\n隊長の差し入れ、きっとあいつら喜びますよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_086_037_00767",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "勘違いしない、あなたのおごりだよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00768",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]